---
description: Frontend UI, Tailwind, and interaction consistency
globs: ["components/**/*", "app/**/*"]
alwaysApply: true
---

## UI/UX

- Clean, modern, minimal design
- Monochrome palette (black/white/gray)
- Strong typography focus

## TAILWIND

- Keep class names readable
- Avoid long messy class chains
- Extract reusable UI patterns

## COMPONENTS

- Reusable and composable
- Keep logic out of UI when possible

## INTERACTIONS

- Smooth hover states
- Micro-interactions on buttons and links
- Consistent spacing and layout system
